id: pm-ol5v
title: "Dangling dependency references: accepted at create/update, skipped by validate, and treated as satisfied by pm next (silent unblock)"
description: ""
type: Issue
status: open
priority: 1
tags: []
created_at: "2026-07-10T17:24:09.633Z"
